{"tid":1808372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"性虐待竟不及石獅子","createTime":"2020-01-02T10:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T01:22:11.000Z","uid":205339,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"98176e102963e7ab65a066bbcce250ffb20f70db","tid":1808372,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:21:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「那是很痛很痛很痛的⋯」<br />\n<br />\n她哭著回憶，在場醫護無人不哭。但讓她更痛的記憶不止如此。阿寶在這場抗爭中與前線10名左右的孩子建立聯繫方式，她花了很多時間和孩子們取得互信，時常請孩子們吃飯。7月底，一名她認識的前線女孩被抓進新屋嶺拘留中心，雖然保全了性命，但不再回應阿寶的任何問題和訊息，亦不接電話。<br />\n<br />\n一日，阿寶在臉書上看見女孩發文：<span style=\"color: green;\">「手足們：我堅持不下去了，你們代我撐下去吧。我會在另一個世界看你。」</span>這是港人過去半年常見的發文，阿寶在恐慌之中到處找人，最後發現女孩自殺未遂。阿寶打聽了許久，女孩最好的朋友才說，<span style=\"color: red;\">女孩曾遭港警性侵，性侵的方式並非使用性器官<br />\n而是警棍⋯</span><br />\n<br />\n台灣鏡週刊原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20191231pol007/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fstory%2F20191231pol007%2F&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=2fb0df1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20191231pol007/</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"45b2c2a80672e5f1f295fd9c7fc2611fd918229f","tid":1808372,"uid":254450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"會輸民意.jpg"},{"pid":"3268f5e60b31400fbdf1474e99a5a0ae2bbcd44f","tid":1808372,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:22:16.000Z","msg":"抗爭者受訪：「那是很痛很痛很痛的⋯」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1806659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1806659</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n一齊推返上熱門<br />\n我們應心存憤怒"},{"pid":"a92ae2457bacd80b6d1325b697fc37139fee0981","tid":1808372,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:22:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f920b5092d943ac85836c453e1af6c2b5c2fc0cf","tid":1808372,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:23:12.000Z","msg":"捉鬼民意撚玩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695c94153e6903cb73b59a3837926931fc5865bb","tid":1808372,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:23:44.000Z","msg":"仲有呢單<br />\n<br />\n《宣戰》<br />\n<br />\n琴晚細牛醫我有個女<br />\n行行下街比人捉左上車<br />\n由上車個一刻幪頭加綁手<br />\n入左差館 , 班狗問佢野佢唔答就踢落佢心口到<br />\n又搣又摸又扯<br />\n仲嘗試過除佢衫 , 想影佢裸照<br />\n塞佢個頭落水盤行水刑<br />\n然後佢唔合作 , 捉番佢上車<br />\n沒收銀包八達通 , 班仆街唔鬆綁<br />\n就咁幪面綁手掉佢係路邊<br />\n我個女無錢番屋企 , 係街到行乞先番到屋企<br />\n<br />\n一星期前有個仔<br />\n番屋企沿路比人捉左上車<br />\n係7人私家狗車 , 一上車就打<br />\n被消失左3日 , 收到風係新屋嶺放番出黎<br />\n<br />\n其他人講 , 你地唔信 <br />\n係我細牛醫本人既病人<br />\n你地信未啊香港人?<br />\n<br />\n黑警 , 我話你地知 , 國難忠醫會企到最後<br />\n國忠所有醫師 , 企穩。<br />\n我地寸土不讓 , 絕對不退。"},{"pid":"7dd90463931931414e59a1c99dcff80f526c060a","tid":1808372,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:25:41.000Z","msg":"大家槍口對外<br />\n唔好再傾捉鬼了"},{"pid":"96442df3f1f5df08c5f6db834b49408a5ec702b5","tid":1808372,"uid":310348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45b2c2a80672e5f1f295fd9c7fc2611fd918229f","tid":1808372,"uid":254450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"會輸民意.jpg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fUUuAYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfUUuAYU.jpg&h=ace64199&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa67e02ffa7a9f4d0074ec1514e202d26ca25352","tid":1808372,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:32:06.000Z","msg":"呢個PO我都有FORWARD，冇咩人推"},{"pid":"90ff7d52176a4d45d8e6fb4f55de5d1e3a542ebe","tid":1808372,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:38:35.000Z","msg":"視覺上嘅衝擊係大過直述<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a2e76523f45b9f642ddd8d8d5bd57ae6c63cfe","tid":1808372,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45b2c2a80672e5f1f295fd9c7fc2611fd918229f","tid":1808372,"uid":254450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"會輸民意.jpg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:41:26.000Z","msg":"連登仔：會輸民意、唔好激嬲中共、唔好搞文物、xx前線好黃唔好搞、唔黑唔好裝修<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa0724c761cb295e55defceec51c26a7e405fc1","tid":1808372,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T01:22:11.000Z","msg":"其實隻獅子燒完都幾型<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809134</a>"}]}